comments:
Yes, I noticed the pattern in the alien words. 

I did not use any specific strategy to recall the words, just tried to remember if it is circle, then should be 'wopykow'. 

I did not use paper to make some notes. 

It's easier for me to remember 'wopykow' and 'zetykow', but I quite struggled to remember 'buvykow' and 'gafykow', especially which one with 'v' and which one with 'f'.
